This package contains a project-internal copy of the root runtime package from:

  github.com/phpdave11/gofpdf v1.4.3

The copied source is used as Paper's internal PDF backend so Paper does not
depend on the external GoFPDF module at build time. The upstream license is
preserved in LICENSE.

Ownership boundary:

  - Treat this directory as third-party-derived backend code.
  - Keep Paper-owned adapter and rendering orchestration logic in
    internal/providers/paper.
  - Avoid casual style-only rewrites or broad refactors in this directory.
  - Record upstream refreshes or local backend patches here.

Local backend patches:

  - 2026-06-05: Modernized the internal backend with dependency-removal
    cleanup, typed CID width generation, first-error-preserving error paths,
    malformed TrueType parser hardening, focused font binary helpers, static
    initialization data helpers, and package-local regression tests.
